OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FGenerally cloudy for most with
OL,6,Fpossibly the odd spot of rain in the
OL,7,Fnorth. Some brighter spells developing
OL,8,Fin the south. Becoming warm as
OL,9,Ftemperatures increase in the south.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FCloudy and settled. In the
OL,12,Fsouth, winds become light and variable
OL,13,Fwith the chance of some mist or fog
OL,14,Fpatches forming under any breaks in
OL,15,Fthe cloud.
OL,16,
OL,17,CMonday:FA mix of cloudy periods and
OL,18,Fsunny spells. Occasionally breezy, and
OL,19,Fbecoming very warm or hot in places as
OL,20,Ftemperatures are likely to gradually
OL,21,Fincrease.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
